{{作品名稱|一個妓女的驚世自白|name=The Happy Hooker: My Own Story}}是荷蘭[[應召女郎|應召女郎]]{{link-nl|薩維拉·賀蘭德|Xaviera Hollander}}於1971年出版的自傳，銷量超過兩千萬本<ref>[http://www.philly.com/inquirer/magazine/20080626_Philmadelphia.html The Philadelphia Inquirer] {{Wayback|url=http://www.philly.com/inquirer/magazine/20080626_Philmadelphia.html |date=20080629004917 }} on ''The Happy Hooker'': "He said he found it fascinating that her book, which has sold 20 million copies to date, is still being picked up today." (26 June 2008)</ref>，這本自傳的內容由傳主口述，羅賓·摩爾（Robin Moore）紀錄了傳主口述的內容，並訂定了書名，而揚尼·旦利維（ Yvonne Dunleavy）改寫口述的內容<ref name=Hollander1971>{{Cite book |title=The Happy Hooker: My Own Story |publisher=Sphere Books |year=1971 |isbn=0-06-001416-4 |last=Hollander |first=Xaviera |url=https://archive.org/details/happyhookermyown00holl }}</ref>或代筆完成該自傳<ref>John Cassidy, "The hell-raiser", ''Sydney Morning Herald'', 9 December 2000, Good Weekend, p. 80</ref>。台灣由新雨出版社於1997年出版，譯者為李信鴻。

== 改編==
賀蘭德的自傳被改編成一系列電影，系列首作是1975年上映、由[[琳恩·蕾格烈芙|琳恩·蕾格烈芙]]主演的《{{link-en|快樂妓女|The Happy Hooker (film)}}》<ref name=NYT1>{{cite web|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|title=The Happy Hooker Details|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/21481/The-Happy-Hooker/details|access-date=2020-08-23|archive-date=2014-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331124746/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/21481/The-Happy-Hooker/details|dead-url=no}}</ref>，第二部作品是1977年上映、由{{link-en|喬伊·希爾頓|Joey Heatherton}}主演的《{{link-en|快樂妓女去華盛頓|The Happy Hooker Goes Washington}}》<ref>{{cite web |title=THE HAPPY HOOKER GOES TO WASHINGTON {{!}} British Board of Film Classification |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/happy-hooker-goes-washington-1970-1 |website=www.bbfc.co.uk |publisher=[[British_Board_of_Film_Classification|British Board of Film Classification]] |accessdate=13 December 2018 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403012103/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/happy-hooker-goes-washington-1970-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，第三部作品是1980年上映、由[[瑪蒂娜·貝斯維克|瑪蒂娜·貝斯維克]]主演的《{{link-en|快樂妓女去好萊塢|The Happy Hooker Goes Hollywood}}》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/DetailView.aspx?s=&Movie=56428 |title=The AFI Catalog of Feature Films:''..The Happy Hooker Goes to Hollywood'' |access-date=2020-08-23 |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215223216/http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/DetailView.aspx?s=&Movie=56428 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

